{"tid":325582,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打想收留一幅zungle眼鏡","createTime":"2017-07-17T10:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T09:03:08.000Z","uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82288d67ee4d3c312a85648715405d4f9adc3e03","tid":325582,"uid":123663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T10:26:26.000Z","msg":"我係kickstarter買左幅zungle眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 姐係個幅透過bone vibrations 將音樂播俾你聽個幅太陽眼鏡，等左成年佢依家終於寄緊俾我，但經過一年我已經㷫過火屎唔想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以諗住睇下有冇巴打想收留左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係我收到應該會寄番番去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我呢幅係白色框跟綠色鏡，送紅色，黑色鏡片一對<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原價出，有心要可以小議<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/105240_957962f2b9bb2f7c58446ffad5f50623.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F105240_957962f2b9bb2f7c58446ffad5f50623.jpg&h=6df22c23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/105244_6429d0fe1047a7025a6be6a50c485c1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F105244_6429d0fe1047a7025a6be6a50c485c1d.jpg&h=3a76189f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/105246_b4e91eb43b1a4275b3368a17e4e65ea7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F17%2F105246_b4e91eb43b1a4275b3368a17e4e65ea7.jpg&h=96e3652c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示意圖：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/17/182555_658308427a654fe6dfaca1ee1509654b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F